137
00:09:55,150 --> 00:09:56,350
Sana cepat!

138
00:09:59,405 --> 00:10:01,400
Lama tidak berjumpa, Da Jeong.

139
00:10:02,300 --> 00:10:03,700
Kabarmu baik?

140
00:10:04,100 --> 00:10:07,000
<i>Han Ji Soo! Song Da Jeong!</i>

141
00:10:12,100 --> 00:10:15,100
Gadis kecil!
Punya wibawa seorang guru juga kau.

142
00:10:19,500 --> 00:10:21,900
<i>Kau menjadi sangat sukses,
Han Ji Soo.</i>

143
